paint me as a slut and a whore.

14:41.864 --> 14:44.365
Believe me, I'm not trying to
publicly do anything with you.

14:44.366 --> 14:46.067
Two million people read
<i>Time.</i> How am I supposed...

14:46.068 --> 14:49.703
