<i> We'd get
soaked right through </i>

01:55:03.545 --> 01:55:09.418
<i> We used to tell them
I was staying at yours </i>

01:55:09.419 --> 01:55:11.253
<i> Sheltered in our own world </i>

01:55:11.254 --> 01:55:13.223
You want to watch from backstage?

01:55:14.723 --> 01:55:16.892
Okay.

