<i> All this time kept
the promise you made </i>

01:56:09.679 --> 01:56:12.947
<i> If you're telling,
I'll be told </i>

01:56:12.948 --> 01:56:17.853
<i> I'll come running and be
there as soon as I can </i>

01:56:20.822 --> 01:56:27.596
<i> Outside of the window,
I was stuck on you </i>

